## Checklist

- [ ] Search bar available on pages with searchable content
- [ ] Debounced search (200-400ms)
- [ ] Clear button in search input
- [ ] No-results state with helpful empty-state text
- [ ] Filters persist in URL
- [ ] Active filter count and chips with removal
- [ ] Clear all filters button
- [ ] Sort indicators on sortable columns
- [ ] Sort and filter parameters validated server-side
- [ ] Search input sanitized (no injection)
- [ ] Searchable fields are indexed in database
- [ ] Pagination on all search results
- [ ] Loading state during search
- [ ] Keyboard shortcut to focus search (Cmd/Ctrl+K)
